==Galician==
===Etymology===
15th century. From older ''geitoso'', from {{suffix|gl|xeito|oso}}. Cognate with {{cog|pt|jeitoso}}.
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|gl|/ʃejˈtoso̝/}}
